# Cursor Dispatch

Use this when the project delegates implementation to Cursor.

Workspace rule source:

- `..\..\System\docs\workflow.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\agent-roles.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\github-pr-rules.md`
- `..\..\System\docs\context-budget.md`

## Dispatch Packet

Each task file should name:

- target branch or PR,
- files allowed to touch,
- files/directories forbidden,
- acceptance checks,
- verify command,
- expected handoff format.

Default rally count is zero. Use one return round only when a narrow fix is
cheaper than local repair. Codex PM owns final adoption, PR review, and merge.
